DTSTAMP:20260515T085337Z
DTSTART:20260511T173000
DTEND:20260511T184500
SUMMARY:W1 Mon · Walk 20–30 min
DESCRIPTION:Plan week 1 · Mon  (weeks 1-8 · Reconditioning + base intro)\nP
 urpose: Activation walk\nWeekly target: 1.5h\n\nJust walk. Brisk pace if y
 ou feel good\, easy stroll if not. 20–30 minutes total. No jogging require
 d. If your knee feels off\, cut it short — there is no penalty.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:to27-w01-tue@training
DTSTAMP:20260515T085337Z
DTSTART:20260512T173000
DTEND:20260512T184500
SUMMARY:W1 Tue · Walk-jog 20 min (30s jog / 90s walk)
DESCRIPTION:Plan week 1 · Tue  (weeks 1-8 · Reconditioning + base intro)\nP
 urpose: First run-walk — get the legs moving\nWeekly target: 1.5h\n\nTotal
  session: 20 minutes.\n\nPattern: jog 30 seconds\, walk 90 seconds\, repea
 t. About 10 cycles.\n\nEffort during the jog: you should be able to talk i
 n full sentences. If you're breathing hard\, slow the jog or take a longer
  walk. The goal is consistency\, not speed. If anything hurts more than mi
 ld discomfort\, stop and walk the rest.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:to27-w01-thu@training
DTSTAMP:20260515T085337Z
DTSTART:20260514T173000
DTEND:20260514T184500
