DESCRIPTION:Plan week 1 · Thu  (weeks 1-8 · Reconditioning + base intro)\nP
 urpose: Recovery walk\nWeekly target: 1.5h\n\nJust walk. Brisk pace if you
  feel good\, easy stroll if not. 20–30 minutes total. No jogging required.
  If your knee feels off\, cut it short — there is no penalty.
END:VEVENT
