BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:to27-w06-sat@training
DTSTAMP:20260515T085337Z
DTSTART:20260620T090000
DTEND:20260620T110000
SUMMARY:W6 Sat · Easy run 30–40 min
DESCRIPTION:Plan week 6 · Sat  (weeks 1-8 · Reconditioning + base intro)\nP
 urpose: Aerobic base\nWeekly target: 3.5h\n\nEasy 30–40 min continuous run
 \, Z2 effort.\n\nZ2 = conversational. Full sentences without gasping. Nose
 -breathing should be possible most of the time. If HR zones aren't set yet
 \, go by feel — when in doubt\, slower. The point of an easy run is to be 
 easy.
END:VEVENT
